snippet.title: THE HIGHWAY KILLER - LARRY EYLER - TRUE CRIME TUESDAYS! | AMBER HOWE
snippet.description:
Hey Babes!

I'm back with another True Crime Tuesday case and todays case is about the Larry Eyler also known as the highway killer or the interstate killer.

Larry William Eyler was an American serial killer who is believed to have murdered a minimum of twenty-one teenage boys and young men in a series of killings committed between 1982 and 1984 in the Midwestern States.
